// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2213 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3941a0a9-dca0-5d55-8f61-76a1b340be2d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
